, \"from\": 796, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines National Velodrome\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"Finucane\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"alien style\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's team\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"their third world record\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not get much better than that, does it?\\\"\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"said Marchant, though in the case of Finucane, in particular, there is expectation, elevated now, that it will.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchant\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"Finucane\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The individual world champion is targeting three gold medals at her debut Olympics, the first of those ticked off on a night that, to a wider public not yet familiar with her name, will have left quite the first impression.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The individual world champion\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"three gold medals\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"her debut Olympics\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"a night\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider public\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the first impression\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To break world records you have to go deeper than your body has ever been before Emma Finucane British track cycling is in need of a new star, having lost the Kennys, Sir Jason and Dame Laura, t